left_text: Cuticle of thorax shining with minute, widely separated punctures; yellow of face pale and inconspicuous; metasomal terga without yellow maculations; worker gonostylus a rounded tubercle with few setae (Fig. 120-6c)
right_text: Cuticle of thorax dull and minutely roughened; paraocular areas largely bright yellow; metasomal terga usually with yellow bands or lateral spots; worker gonostylus about 1.5 times as long as broad, and setose
